<Body>
	<Title>四川成都余震已有四十四次 市民均不愿回家</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年05月12日17:58</ReportTime>　
<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">中新社成都</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">五月十二日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event></Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2">记者</Participant>从四川省地震局<Denoter   type="perception" did="d2">获悉</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e3"><Location lid="l3">成都市</Location>迄今发生<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">余震</Denoter>四十四次，最大震级五点零级。</Event>
			</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event polarity="negative" eid="e4"><Location lid="l4">市区主要街道</Location>没有<Denoter  type="perception" did="d4">看到</Denoter><Object oid="o4">房屋倒塌现象</Object></Event>，但市民均不愿回家。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e5"><Location lid="l5">四川省阿坝州汶川县境内</Location>发生七点八级<Denoter type="emergency" did="d5">地震</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e6"><Location lid="l6">震区</Location>因<Object oid="o6">通讯</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d56">中断</Denoter></Event>仍然没有受灾情况消息；
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e7"><Location lid="l7">绵阳市三台县</Location>因<Object oid="o7">水塔</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d7">倒塌</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e8"><Participant oid="o8">一人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d8">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e9"><Location lid="l9">安县</Location>也有<Participant oid="o9">人员</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">受伤</Denoter></Event>。
			<Event eid="e10"><Participant sid="s10">成都移动</Participant>已开展<Object oid="o10">通讯</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d10">维修</Denoter>工作</Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e11"><Object oid="o11">有关详情</Object>正在进一步<Denoter  type="perception" did="d11">调查了解</Denoter>之中</Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e12">四川省省长<Participant sid="s12">蒋巨峰</Participant>已<Denoter type="operation" did="d12">召集</Denoter><Participant oid="o12">省地震局、省军区、省武警总队</Participant>等单位</Event>
				<Event eid="e13">召开了紧急工作<Denoter type="operation" did="d13">会议</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e14"><Denoter type="operation" did="d14">安排部署</Denoter>了抗震救灾<Object oid="o14">相关工作</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e15">并<Denoter type="operation" did="d15">安排</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16,s18">成都空军</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d16">派遣</Denoter><Object oid="o16,o17">直升机</Object></Event>
				<Event eid="e17"><Denoter type="movement" did="d17">前往</Denoter><Location lid="l17">震区</Location></Event>
				<Event eid="e18"><Denoter  type="perception" did="d18">调查了解</Denoter><Object oid="o18">震情灾情</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">省地震局</Participant>于<Time type="relTime" tid="t19">十二日十五时十五分</Time><Denoter type="operation" did="d19">召开</Denoter>了<Object oid="o19">新闻发布会</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e20">及时将此次地震的<Object oid="o20">震情灾情</Object>向新闻媒体作了<Denoter  type="perception" did="d20">通报</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e21"><Time type="relTime" tid="t21">目前</Time>，<Participant sid="s21">四川省地震局</Participant>正抓紧<Denoter type="operation" did="d21">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o21">震后趋势会商工作</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
